    <h1>Grilled Lemon Herb Chicken</h1>

    <!-- <img src="" alt=""> -->

    <h2>Description</h2>

    <p>
        Savor the bright, zesty flavors of Grilled Lemon Herb Chicken in this simple yet delicious recipe.
    </p>

    <p>
        Marinated in a mixture of lemon, garlic, and fresh herbs, this chicken is grilled to perfection, resulting in tender, juicy, and flavorful poultry that's perfect for any occasion.
    </p>

    <h2>Ingredients</h2>

    <ul>
        <li>4 boneless, skinless chicken breasts</li>
        <li>Zest and juice of 2 lemons</li>
        <li>4 garlic cloves, minced</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons fresh rosemary, chopped</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons fresh thyme, chopped</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons fresh parsley, chopped</li>
        <li>1/4 cup olive oil</li>
        <li>Salt and black pepper, to taste</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Steps</h2>

    <ol>
        <li>Marinate the Chicken</li>

        <li>Preheat and Oil the Grill</li>

        <li>Grill the Chicken</li>

        <li>Rest and Garnish</li>
    </ol>
</body>
